// ActivityPub federation tests
//
// Tests that REST mutations (create, update, delete) generate correct
// ActivityPub activities in the outbox, and that the server inbox can
// receive and process incoming Create / Update / Delete activities from
// federated peers.
//
// The tests simulate multi-instance federation by:
// 1. Performing a REST mutation (representing "Instance A")
// 2. Reading the outbox to capture the generated activity
// 3. POSTing that activity to the server inbox (simulating "Instance B" receiving it)
// 4. Verifying the inbox processed the activity correctly

